# subtask.rc
# Taskwarrior configuration for tw-subtask-hook
# Version: 1.0.0
#
# No UDAs are required — parent/child relationships are tracked via the
# native dep: field and the UUID embedded in the annotation line.
#
# Include this file from ~/.taskrc if you want a central place for future
# subtask-related configuration:
#
#   include ~/.task/config/subtask.rc
